<body>
<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="11800000t" end="34800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">你们这群胆小鬼</p>
<p begin="41600000t" end="81200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">乖乖闭上嘴把所有一切都投资在我身上就对了！</p>
<p begin="141200000t" end="157000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">你现在最需要的是</p>
<p begin="164400000t" end="190000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">不是语言上的「教育」而是「教训」</p>
<p begin="218800000t" end="233200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">结论已定</p>
<p begin="246200000t" end="271600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">艾连被调查兵团接管</p>
<p begin="276600000t" end="301600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">用于进行墙外调查</p>
<p begin="330800000t" end="370400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">Wohlan Freund! Jetzt hier ist ein Sieg.</p>
<p begin="330800000t" end="370400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">来吧战友！ 这是一场胜利</p>
<p begin="370400000t" end="401400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">Dies ist der erste Gloria.</p>
<p begin="370400000t" end="401400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">亦是初尝的光荣胜果</p>
<p begin="401400000t" end="410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">O mein Freund!</p>
<p begin="401400000t" end="410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">吾之战友啊！</p>
<p begin="410000000t" end="465000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">Feiern wir dieser Sieg für der nächsten Kampf!</p>
<p begin="410000000t" end="465000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">为了下一场胜利  举杯欢庆吧！</p>
<p begin="610600000t" end="664400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">「無意味な死であった」と…言わせない</p>
<p begin="610600000t" end="664400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">世上不存在「毫无价值的牺牲」</p>
<p begin="666200000t" end="729400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">最後の《一矢》になるまで……</p>
<p begin="666200000t" end="729400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">即便只剩孤身一人亦在所不惜</p>
<p begin="718000000t" end="747400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">Der feind ist grausam… Wir bringen…</p>
<p begin="718000000t" end="747400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">敌人如此残酷  我们将其扫除</p>
<p begin="747400000t" end="778200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">Der feind ist riesig…Wir springen…</p>
<p begin="747400000t" end="778200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">敌人如此巨大  我们将其粉碎</p>
<p begin="778200000t" end="836600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">両手には《鋼刃》　唄うのは《凱歌》</p>
<p begin="778200000t" end="836600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">双手紧握《钢刃》心中高奏《凯歌》</p>
<p begin="836600000t" end="883800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">背中には《自由の翼》</p>
<p begin="836600000t" end="883800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">身后飘舞《自由之翼》</p>
<p begin="897800000t" end="958200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">握り締めた決意を左胸に</p>
<p begin="897800000t" end="958200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">将坚定的信念置于胸前</p>
<p begin="959800000t" end="1004600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">斬り裂くのは《愚行の螺旋》</p>
<p begin="959800000t" end="1004600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">斩断一切《愚昧螺旋》</p>
<p begin="1018800000t" end="1083600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">蒼穹を舞う――自由の翼</p>
<p begin="1018800000t" end="1083600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">愿自由之翼翱翔于苍穹</p>
<p begin="1224900000t" end="1274900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">特别作战小队</p>
<p begin="1279900000t" end="1327800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">托洛斯特区</p>
<p begin="1395100000t" end="1415300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">旧调查兵团本部</p>
<p begin="1438100000t" end="1463100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">不愧是古堡改建而成的设施</p>
<p begin="1467900000t" end="1490700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">单论情调那绝对是一流的</p>
<p begin="1502700000t" end="1540300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">不过在这种远离城墙和河流的地方建立的本部</p>
<p begin="1546700000t" end="1572300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">对调查兵团来说毫无用处</p>
<p begin="1586900000t" end="1621900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">这是过去那支空有一腔抱负的调查兵团刚成立时的事情了</p>
<p begin="1632700000t" end="1694100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">不过没想到这个超大装饰品居然会成为最适合看守你的建筑</p>
<p begin="1733700000t" end="1750900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">不要得意忘形  新兵</p>
<p begin="1753300000t" end="1757900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">什么？</p>
<p begin="1768100000t" end="1785900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">我不管你是不是巨人</p>
<p begin="1789300000t" end="1833500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">但居然要劳烦里维士官长整天守着你这种乳臭未干的小子…</p>
<p begin="1883500000t" end="1911700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">骑马时说个不停当然会咬到舌头了</p>
<p begin="1918500000t" end="1930300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">开头才是关键</p>
<p begin="1936300000t" end="1955300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">那个新人被吓到了呢</p>
<p begin="1959700000t" end="1990700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">我想他只是被你的蠢劲吓到而已</p>
<p begin="1997100000t" end="2028700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">不管怎么说  一切都按我预期的方向发展了</p>
<p begin="2035700000t" end="2069700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">我说  你过去不是这么说话的吧</p>
<p begin="2081100000t" end="2086500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">如果…</p>
<p begin="2091100000t" end="2122900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">如果你是在学里维士官长</p>
<p begin="2125700000t" end="2140500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">那我真心求你别再学了</p>
<p begin="2144700000t" end="2174900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">不  我完全感觉不到你们有共通点</p>
<p begin="2190500000t" end="2212500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">你想束缚我吗  佩托拉</p>
<p begin="2216900000t" end="2254900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">你若是想以我的妻子自居  还少了一道必要手续呢</p>
<p begin="2264100000t" end="2284900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">你怎么不咬断舌头死掉啊…</p>
<p begin="2291300000t" end="2315900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">总是到处吹嘘你那些讨伐巨人的破事儿</p>
<p begin="2320900000t" end="2363100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">放心吧  我也有顺便夸你们</p>
<p begin="2381100000t" end="2417700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">那些人就是调查兵团特别作战小队</p>
<p begin="2425700000t" end="2438500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">通称里维小队</p>
<p begin="2443500000t" end="2458300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">你真是不像样</p>
<p begin="2466300000t" end="2475300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">佩托拉·拉尔</p>
<p begin="2480500000t" end="2495700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">讨伐巨人数10只</p>
<p begin="2498900000t" end="2517500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">协助讨伐数48只</p>
<p begin="2533100000t" end="2543300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">欧鲁·波札德</p>
<p begin="2547900000t" end="2560900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">讨伐39只</p>
<p begin="2563500000t" end="2577300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">协助讨伐9只</p>
<p begin="2587900000t" end="2601100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">都是如假包换的精英</p>
<p begin="2632500000t" end="2639500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">艾鲁多·琴</p>
<p begin="2643900000t" end="2655500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">讨伐14只</p>
<p begin="2658300000t" end="2673700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">协助讨伐32只</p>
<p begin="2684300000t" end="2694100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">君达·修兹</p>
<p begin="2698300000t" end="2708300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">讨伐7只</p>
<p begin="2709900000t" end="2723700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">协助讨伐40只</p>
<p begin="2744100000t" end="2763900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">这些人都是里维士官长亲自点名的</p>
<p begin="2766500000t" end="2784700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">调查兵团中的顶级精英</p>
<p begin="2791700000t" end="2827500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">而在我失控时</p>
<p begin="2835900000t" end="2856700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">我就会被他们杀掉</p>
<p begin="2879900000t" end="2896900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">到处都是杂草啊</p>
<p begin="2902900000t" end="2916500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">真荒凉啊</p>
<p begin="2919900000t" end="2939100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">毕竟我们很久没使用这里了</p>
<p begin="2944100000t" end="2960500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">想必里面也一定是积满了灰尘吧</p>
<p begin="2964300000t" end="2991100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">那可是个重大问题啊</p>
<p begin="3004900000t" end="3021100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">立即开始清理</p>
<p begin="3115500000t" end="3136900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">上层的清扫已经完毕</p>
<p begin="3156100000t" end="3181300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">我应该睡在这个设施的什么地方呢</p>
<p begin="3198100000t" end="3215300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">你的房间在地下室</p>
<p begin="3222100000t" end="3242500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">又是地下室吗…</p>
<p begin="3245900000t" end="3254300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">当然了</p>
<p begin="3261900000t" end="3285500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">你现在还没法控制自己</p>
<p begin="3297300000t" end="3312700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">如果你睡迷糊了变成巨人</p>
<p begin="3315900000t" end="3338100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">而那里正好就是地下  我们可以当场将你抓住</p>
<p begin="3344700000t" end="3387500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">这是把你列入我方管辖之时  上头提出的条件之一</p>
<p begin="3392300000t" end="3404500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">是必须遵守的规则</p>
<p begin="3435300000t" end="3444900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">我去看看你打扫的房间</p>
<p begin="3451300000t" end="3471700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">艾连  你来打扫这里</p>
<p begin="3474100000t" end="3479100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">好的</p>
<p begin="3543700000t" end="3562300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">你一脸失望的表情呢  艾连</p>
<p begin="3564500000t" end="3571700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">什么？</p>
<p begin="3580100000t" end="3594500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">我以后就叫你艾连了</p>
<p begin="3598300000t" end="3613500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">学里维士官长的叫法</p>
<p begin="3620300000t" end="3638700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">因为在这里士官长就是规则</p>
<p begin="3646100000t" end="3671500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">好的  这我倒不介意</p>
<p begin="3676100000t" end="3701100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">不过我刚才露出失望的表情了吗</p>
<p begin="3705300000t" end="3720900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">这不是什么稀奇的反应啦</p>
<p begin="3728300000t" end="3764100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">他看上去不像传说中那位完美无瑕的英雄吧</p>
<p begin="3769700000t" end="3784700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">现实中的里维士官长…</p>
<p begin="3797900000t" end="3811900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">不但个子出奇的矮小</p>
<p begin="3814900000t" end="3839500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">而且既神经质又粗暴  难以亲近</p>
<p begin="3851100000t" end="3909500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">不  让我意外的是他那种对于上头规定绝对服从的姿态</p>
<p begin="3916700000t" end="3932500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">因为他是非常有实力的人</p>
<p begin="3934300000t" end="3959100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">所以你觉得他不是那种会循规蹈矩的人？</p>
<p begin="3966100000t" end="3971500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">没错</p>
<p begin="3982300000t" end="4006500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">我以为他是那种不会理会任何指示的人…</p>
<p begin="4015500000t" end="4034900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">虽然我知道的也不多</p>
<p begin="4040500000t" end="4065900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">不过我猜过去的他可能和你说的很接近吧</p>
<p begin="4081300000t" end="4107900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">听说里维士官长在加入调查兵团前</p>
<p begin="4112500000t" end="4139100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">是王都地下街有名的小混混</p>
<p begin="4155900000t" end="4174100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">那种人为何会…</p>
<p begin="4180900000t" end="4189300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">谁知道呢</p>
<p begin="4195100000t" end="4211500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">虽然我不知道发生了什么</p>
<p begin="4217500000t" end="4262900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">不过我听说他是以被艾尔文团长收服的形式带回调查兵团的</p>
<p begin="4279300000t" end="4286500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">被团长？</p>
<p begin="4299100000t" end="4309900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">喂  艾连</p>
<p begin="4316700000t" end="4322100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">在！</p>
<p begin="4331700000t" end="4343900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">完全没打扫干净</p>
<p begin="4346900000t" end="4362500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">给我全部重新打扫一遍</p>
<p begin="4393500000t" end="4429700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">30天后进行墙外远征以建立兵站据点吗</p>
<p begin="4441900000t" end="4468700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">而且还带上这一期刚毕业的新兵</p>
<p begin="4477700000t" end="4497100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">前提是真的有新兵肯入我们团</p>
<p begin="4515300000t" end="4550900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">总之我觉得你有些操之过急了</p>
<p begin="4562500000t" end="4593100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">艾连现在的待遇只是暂时性的</p>
<p begin="4599700000t" end="4650700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">我们必须尽可能快地让中央明白  他是对人类十分有用的存在</p>
<p begin="4664300000t" end="4701700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">不然的话  不知什么时候宪兵团又会来插手</p>
<p begin="4701700000t" end="4725900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">你对我也要讲这些场面话吗  艾尔文</p>
<p begin="4789500000t" end="4812500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">你的嗅觉总是那么敏锐  米可</p>
<p begin="4829900000t" end="4853100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">不过还远远及不上你</p>
<p begin="4870500000t" end="4884700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">等时机到了我自然会说</p>
<p begin="4966900000t" end="4999500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">对我们下达的待机命令大概还会持续几天</p>
<p begin="5006700000t" end="5044100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">我听说30天后可能会有大规模墙外远征的计划</p>
<p begin="5054100000t" end="5089500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">听说本期刚毕业的新兵也将被立刻投入行动</p>
<p begin="5095300000t" end="5109700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">你说的是真的吗  艾鲁多</p>
<p begin="5114100000t" end="5128900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">这事来的还真是突然啊</p>
<p begin="5137890000t" end="5181100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">光是这次的巨人袭击就给了新兵一次下马威</p>
<p begin="5190100000t" end="5217500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">小鬼们肯定完全吓尿了呢</p>
<p begin="5223300000t" end="5236100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">这是真的吗  士官长</p>
<p begin="5238300000t" end="5265300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">我不是负责制定作战计划的人</p>
<p begin="5274300000t" end="5290100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">不过艾尔文这人你们也清楚</p>
<p begin="5294900000t" end="5319100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">他肯定比我们要想的深得多吧</p>
<p begin="5325500000t" end="5359900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">确实这次和以往的情况有所不同呢</p>
<p begin="5367100000t" end="5402100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">才以为付出巨大牺牲而开辟出的夺回玛利亚的路线</p>
<p begin="5404500000t" end="5425300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">已经瞬间化为白纸一张…</p>
<p begin="5427900000t" end="5457900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">可结果眼前突然又冒出了一个新希望</p>
<p begin="5546100000t" end="5564100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">虽然到现在我还无法相信</p>
<p begin="5571500000t" end="5606900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">不过「变成巨人」是什么感觉啊  艾连</p>
<p begin="5619300000t" end="5648300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">那时的记忆并不是十分清晰</p>
<p begin="5656300000t" end="5672300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">总之我想的只有一件事</p>
<p begin="5681300000t" end="5708900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">不过变身的契机是自残行为</p>
<p begin="5714700000t" end="5727900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">像这样咬破手…</p>
<p begin="5733900000t" end="5776300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">咦  说起来我怎么会知道这么多</p>
<p begin="5789900000t" end="5804300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">想必你们也知道吧</p>
<p begin="5812700000t" end="5833100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">从他口里是问不出报告书之外的内容的</p>
<p begin="5840700000t" end="5866900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">不过  那家伙应该闲不住吧</p>
<p begin="5895700000t" end="5919900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">一不小心说不定会被那家伙玩死哦</p>
<p begin="5921700000t" end="5941700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">说的就是你  艾连</p>
<p begin="5951700000t" end="5958900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">「那家伙」是？</p>
<p begin="6010700000t" end="6044300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">晚上好  里维小队的各位</p>
<p begin="6051500000t" end="6071700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">住在城堡中感觉如何啊</p>
<p begin="6075300000t" end="6084700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">真快啊</p>
<p begin="6088300000t" end="6110500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">因为我实在等不及了啊</p>
<p begin="6114900000t" end="6128500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">汉吉分队长</p>
<p begin="6131900000t" end="6142500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">久等了  艾连</p>
<p begin="6152100000t" end="6203100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">我现在负责对城里抓到的两只巨人进行活体调查</p>
<p begin="6206500000t" end="6235100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">不过明天的实验我希望艾连也能帮我个忙</p>
<p begin="6239300000t" end="6253900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">我是来征求你的许可的</p>
<p begin="6262300000t" end="6278900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">实验吗…</p>
<p begin="6288300000t" end="6297300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">你要我做什么…</p>
<p begin="6297300000t" end="6307500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">那当然是…</p>
<p begin="6315100000t" end="6344300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">最让人热血沸腾的那个啦</p>
<p begin="6348500000t" end="6358900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">啊  那个…</p>
<p begin="6363300000t" end="6387500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">我自己无法下达许可</p>
<p begin="6396700000t" end="6425500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">因为我的处置权不在我自己手上</p>
<p begin="6426900000t" end="6448300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">里维  明天艾连有预定吗</p>
<p begin="6457300000t" end="6468500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">清扫庭院</p>
<p begin="6468500000t" end="6481300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">那就好</p>
<p begin="6485100000t" end="6492300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">决定了</p>
<p begin="6513900000t" end="6532500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">艾连  明天请多指教</p>
<p begin="6547500000t" end="6553900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">好的</p>
<p begin="6564100000t" end="6595300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">不过  拿巨人进行的实验都干些什么啊</p>
<p begin="6622700000t" end="6627300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">那个…</p>
<p begin="6632900000t" end="6646700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">巨人的实验是…</p>
<p begin="6646700000t" end="6660300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">喂  快住口  别问了</p>
<p begin="6667300000t" end="6690100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">啊  果然想听？</p>
<p begin="6697100000t" end="6726500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">我早就看出你一副想要问的表情</p>
<p begin="6839700000t" end="6860500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">你这么想听吗</p>
<p begin="6865700000t" end="6880300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">真拿你没办法</p>
<p begin="6888500000t" end="6909900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">那我就得好好讲一讲呢</p>
<p begin="6920700000t" end="6955300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">关于这次我们抓到的那些孩子们的事</p>
<p begin="6920700000t" end="6955300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">巨人们</p>
<p begin="6965200000t" end="7015200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">▇</p>
<p begin="6965200000t" end="7015200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">目前可以公开的情报</p>
<p begin="7015300000t" end="7065200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">▇</p>
<p begin="7015300000t" end="7065200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">目前可以公开的情报</p>
<p begin="7080600000t" end="7131000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">首先从过去5次捕获都反覆进行的实验开始</p>
<p begin="7160200000t" end="7168200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">你好啊</p>
<p begin="7200000000t" end="7228800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">一开始是对「意思沟通」进行检验</p>
<p begin="7239400000t" end="7249600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">感觉如何</p>
<p begin="7257000000t" end="7281200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">你叫什么名字  身体疼吗？</p>
<p begin="7291000000t" end="7307400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">分队长  你靠得太近了</p>
<p begin="7336200000t" end="7347000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">你好</p>
<p begin="7354600000t" end="7376400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">天气真好啊  你饿了吗？</p>
<p begin="7398400000t" end="7417000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">好险  太险了</p>
<p begin="7417000000t" end="7431600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">分队长  这太危险了</p>
<p begin="7436600000t" end="7448800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">令人遗憾的是</p>
<p begin="7453400000t" end="7493200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">这次得出的结论仍然是不可能进行沟通</p>
<p begin="7521400000t" end="7548200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">但是对我来说  与巨人的交流</p>
<p begin="7552800000t" end="7591600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">足以令我忘记每天的疲劳  是十分充实的时光</p>
<p begin="7608000000t" end="7655200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">很久之前  某个地方存在着吃人一族</p>
<p begin="7672000000t" end="7710600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">不是指你们巨人哦  而是人类中的一族</p>
<p begin="7720000000t" end="7752800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">他们藏身于山腰的洞窟之中</p>
<p begin="7758600000t" end="7798000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">袭击路过的旅客  抢夺其财物</p>
<p begin="7800200000t" end="7827000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">最后将其杀死  并且吃掉他的肉</p>
<p begin="7837600000t" end="7868400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">又来了啊  分队长的命名仪式</p>
<p begin="7872400000t" end="7897200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">嗯  上次是什么来着</p>
<p begin="7898800000t" end="7917600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">吉卡基罗尼和阿尔贝特</p>
<p begin="7922200000t" end="7971800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">从结果来看  他们这种罪行一直持续了25年</p>
<p begin="7977000000t" end="8018000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">在此期间  据说被害者超过了500人</p>
<p begin="8029400000t" end="8065800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">这恐怕比你们吃掉的人类还多吧</p>
<p begin="8077800000t" end="8112400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">另外  他们还尝试了各种吃人的方法</p>
<p begin="8122400000t" end="8138400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">臀部的肉烤成肉排</p>
<p begin="8148400000t" end="8174600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">大腿肉切块放入炖菜中</p>
<p begin="8180600000t" end="8212600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">较硬的肉绞碎后揉成肉饼再拿去烤</p>
<p begin="8218200000t" end="8251800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">他们还用血块和内脏做了香肠</p>
<p begin="8258800000t" end="8296600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">没错  他们有烹饪的概念</p>
<p begin="8300800000t" end="8321400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">这就是与你们的不同之处</p>
<p begin="8332400000t" end="8375400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">但是吃人一族仅仅因为一个小失误而被抓</p>
<p begin="8376600000t" end="8388600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">最后被判以死刑</p>
<p begin="8399600000t" end="8419800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">这就和你们一样</p>
<p begin="8426800000t" end="8460800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">攻击人类就是你们的失误</p>
<p begin="8462600000t" end="8477200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">而你们也因此被抓</p>
<p begin="8495200000t" end="8551400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">因此  我想把吃人一族首领的名字赐予你们</p>
<p begin="8560400000t" end="8573000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">你叫「索尼」</p>
<p begin="8582800000t" end="8596000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">你就叫「宾」</p>
<p begin="8614600000t" end="8625600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">但是你们大可放心</p>
<p begin="8632000000t" end="8659200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">我是不会杀掉你们的</p>
<p begin="8670400000t" end="8681000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">请多关照  索尼</p>
<p begin="8688800000t" end="8700200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">宾也是</p>
<p begin="8715800000t" end="8729400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">大家好好相处吧</p>
<p begin="8750200000t" end="8774000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">就这样  我把7米级的取名为「宾」</p>
<p begin="8779200000t" end="8810200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">4米级的取名为「索尼」</p>
<p begin="8863000000t" end="8891400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">接下来进行了「遮蔽阳光」的实验</p>
<p begin="8900800000t" end="8929800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">因为入夜之后巨人的活动力会下降</p>
<p begin="8932800000t" end="8981800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">这个实验证明巨人从阳光中获得了某种活动力</p>
<p begin="8993200000t" end="9022600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">结论是巨人存在很大的个体差异</p>
<p begin="9034600000t" end="9060400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">嗯  你很努力呢索尼</p>
<p begin="9072400000t" end="9093000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">晚安  明天见</p>
<p begin="9105600000t" end="9151600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">遮蔽阳光后1小时  索尼的活动能力明显下降</p>
<p begin="9161000000t" end="9193400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">你可真喜欢熬夜啊  宾</p>
<p begin="9203200000t" end="9231800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">没问题  我也会奉陪到底的</p>
<p begin="9248200000t" end="9274000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">相比之下宾过了3小时依然很有活力</p>
<p begin="9310800000t" end="9329000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">再次让我吃了一惊</p>
<p begin="9335800000t" end="9356000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">它们不需要喝水进食</p>
<p begin="9361000000t" end="9390000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">尽管有发声器官  却不需要呼吸</p>
<p begin="9396800000t" end="9426400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">唯一的动力来源竟然是「阳光」</p>
<p begin="9437800000t" end="9458400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">我也很想知道一直遮蔽阳光最后会怎么样</p>
<p begin="9464400000t" end="9491400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">但它们要是死了就伤脑筋了呢</p>
<p begin="9505400000t" end="9539800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">之前捕获的孩子  被我不小心杀死了</p>
<p begin="9550400000t" end="9588000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">在砍头实验中不小心把后颈也削掉了</p>
<p begin="9595200000t" end="9626600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">名字叫吉卡基罗尼和阿尔贝特</p>
<p begin="9638600000t" end="9656400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">那两个孩子笑起来很可爱呢</p>
<p begin="9668200000t" end="9697600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">我真的很对不起它们</p>
<p begin="9722000000t" end="9750600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">再也不想重蹈覆辙了</p>
<p begin="9772600000t" end="9786800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">汉吉分队长</p>
<p begin="9815800000t" end="9855800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">接着  下个阶段将直接与巨人的身体接触</p>
<p begin="9859600000t" end="9886600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">试验进入了「确认痛觉」阶段</p>
<p begin="9955800000t" end="9978800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">分队长  你没必要一起喊啊…</p>
<p begin="9979800000t" end="9997400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">我怎么能不喊啊</p>
<p begin="10001800000t" end="10032000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">宾可是这么的疼啊</p>
<p begin="10039000000t" end="10079400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">宾  加油啊  你要撑下去！</p>
<p begin="10094400000t" end="10142000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">毕竟我们需要确认巨人是否存在「后颈」以外的弱点</p>
<p begin="10157000000t" end="10172600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">这种工作真令人煎熬</p>
<p begin="10201000000t" end="10240200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">索尼  我在刺你的心脏啊</p>
<p begin="10245990000t" end="10272000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">不疼吗  感觉如何</p>
<p begin="10285400000t" end="10317200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">与宾相比  索尼性格比较内向</p>
<p begin="10323800000t" end="10341190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">并没有表现出什么反应</p>
<p begin="10365790000t" end="10383800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">什么？你怎么了？</p>
<p begin="10418190000t" end="10435790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">分队长  请你退后</p>
<p begin="10458590000t" end="10483190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">刚才真是可惜啊  索尼</p>
<p begin="10476190000t" end="10493200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">你真的会死的啊</p>
<p begin="10510800000t" end="10548600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">索尼它不擅长表现自己</p>
<p begin="10555400000t" end="10577800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">老是想咬别人的头</p>
<p begin="10580600000t" end="10594800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">那个  汉吉分队长</p>
<p begin="10602000000t" end="10605800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">嗯？</p>
<p begin="10613400000t" end="10657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">为什么你面对巨人还可以这么开朗呢</p>
<p begin="10685600000t" end="10740200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">巨人是把我们人类逼到近乎灭亡的天敌</p>
<p begin="10750600000t" end="10791600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">您也应该体验过无数次这种威胁才对…</p>
<p begin="10808600000t" end="10863600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">没错  我曾无数次目睹同伴被巨人杀害</p>
<p begin="10877200000t" end="10923800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">刚进入调查兵团时  我凭藉着恨意与巨人战斗</p>
<p begin="10937800000t" end="10966000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">但某一天我突然发现了</p>
<p begin="10982000000t" end="11017200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">那是在我踢飞一颗被切断的3米级巨人头颅的时候</p>
<p begin="11036200000t" end="11081200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">我发现巨人的身体…异常的轻啊</p>
<p begin="11105400000t" end="11167400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">本来巨人的庞大身躯根本不可能用双脚支撑并行走</p>
<p begin="11178600000t" end="11193000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">每个巨人都是这样</p>
<p begin="11201800000t" end="11249600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">切断的手臂都达不到其应有的重量</p>
<p begin="11261400000t" end="11278800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">我听说艾连你变成巨人的时候</p>
<p begin="11282200000t" end="11318600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">巨人的身体也是凭空出现</p>
<p begin="11341600000t" end="11354600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">于是我在想…</p>
<p begin="11365600000t" end="11398800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">我们所看见的东西与实际存在的东西…</p>
<p begin="11403400000t" end="11424400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">本质会不会截然不同呢</p>
<p begin="11475200000t" end="11525000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">这几十年来我们一直尝试着用仇恨来对抗巨人</p>
<p begin="11539200000t" end="11583800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">我想从现存观念以外的观点来看待巨人</p>
<p begin="11598200000t" end="11617000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">或许这可能徒劳无功</p>
<p begin="11627800000t" end="11655000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">但是  我还是会尝试</p>
<p begin="11734800000t" end="11769400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">进入调查兵团后  碰到的都是令我惊讶的事</p>
<p begin="11780400000t" end="11810400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">不只是汉吉分队长  每个人都是怪人</p>
<p begin="11821200000t" end="11846600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">这里就像是…怪人的巢穴</p>
<p begin="11857000000t" end="11862600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">但是</p>
<p begin="11875600000t" end="11895600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">寻求变革的人类集团</p>
<p begin="11903200000t" end="11922000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">这才是调查兵团的真面目</p>
<p begin="11937600000t" end="11944000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">汉吉分队长</p>
<p begin="11959400000t" end="11999200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">不介意的话  能否把更多关于实验的事讲给我听呢</p>
<p begin="12003200000t" end="12017800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">咦  你想听吗</p>
<p begin="12020400000t" end="12025800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">是</p>
<p begin="12030600000t" end="12071200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">为了明天的实验我也想了解得更详细些</p>
<p begin="12080200000t" end="12095600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">说…说得也是</p>
<p begin="12109800000t" end="12139000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">刚才我说的有很多地方都省略了</p>
<p begin="12142600000t" end="12180000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">我就再说详细些吧  虽然可能会有点长…</p>
<p begin="12181400000t" end="12185800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">没关系</p>
<p begin="12191600000t" end="12241000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">首先是刚捕获到巨人时  我是这样假设的…</p>
<p begin="12271600000t" end="12317200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">所以这次的实验并未获得任何新情报…</p>
<p begin="12326200000t" end="12362600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">刚才说的  在你还是训练兵时就应该听过了</p>
<p begin="12365800000t" end="12378800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">艾连应该也知道吧</p>
<p begin="12388000000t" end="12411400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">是  我全部都知道</p>
<p begin="12417400000t" end="12468000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">所以接下来我会加入个人的见解  再次解读一遍哦</p>
<p begin="12468800000t" end="12493600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">诶  那个  已经…</p>
<p begin="12491000000t" end="12501200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">首先是与巨人的…</p>
<p begin="12511200000t" end="12525800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">汉吉分队长在吗！</p>
<p begin="12535400000t" end="12572200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">实验体…两只巨人都被杀死了</p>
<p begin="12675200000t" end="12697200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">索尼  宾</p>
<p begin="12703400000t" end="12740800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">骗人的  告诉我这是骗人的！</p>
<p begin="12760000000t" end="12776400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">居然把珍贵的实验体杀了…</p>
<p begin="12782800000t" end="12794200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">是士兵干的吗</p>
<p begin="12796800000t" end="12822200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">嗯  目前还没有抓到犯人</p>
<p begin="12831000000t" end="12852400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">好像是在天亮之前同时被杀的</p>
<p begin="12858400000t" end="12894600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">守卫发现时  犯人已经用立体机动逃跑了</p>
<p begin="12901400000t" end="12930000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">是两人以上有预谋的行动吗</p>
<p begin="12938800000t" end="12952000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">索尼</p>
<p begin="12953600000t" end="12987200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">你们看  汉吉分队长发狂了</p>
<p begin="13013200000t" end="13030200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">这到底是…</p>
<p begin="13037800000t" end="13066600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">我们走  接下来是宪兵团的工作</p>
<p begin="13072400000t" end="13079400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">是</p>
<p begin="13117800000t" end="13131800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">你能看出什么吗？</p>
<p begin="13164000000t" end="13176400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">你认为敌人是谁？</p>
<p begin="13227600000t" end="13252200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">抱歉  问了些奇怪的问题</p>
<p begin="13305000000t" end="13345000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">本字幕由 动漫国字幕组&恶魔岛字幕组 联合制作</p>
<p begin="13345000000t" end="13385000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">翻译:小呆&小呓  校对:TL旧民  特效:Re·write  后期:EinAlive  MKV:Holy</p>
<p begin="13566400000t" end="13618400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">例えば俺が俺じゃないとして</p>
<p begin="13566400000t" end="13618400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">如果说我不是我</p>
<p begin="13619000000t" end="13669800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">お前はお前だと言いきれるのか</p>
<p begin="13619000000t" end="13669800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">那么你能确定你就是你吗</p>
<p begin="13670600000t" end="13722000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">砂の器を壊してこぼれた</p>
<p begin="13670600000t" end="13722000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">破裂器皿  细沙不断洒落</p>
<p begin="13722600000t" end="13775000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">心を拾って集められるか</p>
<p begin="13722600000t" end="13775000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">心如碎屑  试问如何聚拢</p>
<p begin="13775000000t" end="13866200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">誰かの呼ぶ声が耳鳴に変わった</p>
<p begin="13775000000t" end="13866200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">未名呼唤  化作阵阵耳鸣</p>
<p begin="13866200000t" end="13917600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">時が止まったみたいだ</p>
<p begin="13866200000t" end="13917600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">似乎连时间都为之停止</p>
<p begin="13917600000t" end="13946000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">さあ　目を覚ませ</p>
<p begin="13917600000t" end="13946000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">来吧  苏醒吧</p>
<p begin="13946600000t" end="13995200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">深い闇を俺は抜け出した</p>
<p begin="13946600000t" end="13995200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">我逃出了深邃的黑暗</p>
<p begin="13998200000t" end="14046800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">疾風みたいに逃げ出した</p>
<p begin="13998200000t" end="14046800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">快得犹如一阵疾风</p>
<p begin="14050800000t" end="14095600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">生きた屍みたいだった</p>
<p begin="14050800000t" end="14095600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">告别行尸走肉般的生活</p>
<p begin="14096800000t" end="14165800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">俺達は壁の外へまた会おうぜ</p>
<p begin="14096800000t" end="14165800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">我们在墙外再会吧</p>
<p begin="14166400000t" end="14208200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">地図にない場所で</p>
<p begin="14166400000t" end="14208200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">在地图没标记的地方</p>
<p begin="14338400000t" end="14378800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">在搜寻杀死索尼和宾的犯人的同时</p>
<p begin="14384000000t" end="14416400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">三笠和阿尔敏等  第104期训练兵</p>
<p begin="14417800000t" end="14465800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">怀着各自的思绪  面临所属兵团的抉择</p>
<p begin="14457700000t" end="14474700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">如今应做何事</p>
